    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a superlative 2004 BMW M3 featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six power plant. This high-revving unit utilizes individual throttle bodies and double VANOS to deliver linear power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. Mated to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, the drivetrain is complemented by a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis is in concourse-level condition, with documented subframe reinforcement and a full suspension refresh utilizing OEM bushings to maintain factory kinematics. The atmospheric induction note is crisp, the throttle response is telepathic, and the exterior retains its original paint depth with no signs of oxidation or panel misalignment. This is a turn-key collector-grade specimen for the purist who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
