    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality vehicle that satisfies even the most discerning collector. This car has been meticulously garaged and maintained with an open-checkbook philosophy. The exterior paint retains its deep, mirror-like luster, protected by a professional ceramic coating; you will find zero stone chips, swirl marks, or door dings. Inside, the cabin remains in factory-fresh condition, featuring supple, unscuffed leather and that distinct 'new car' scent. Every electronic component, from the premium sound system to the climate control, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a full, documented service history from authorized dealerships. The engine bay is immaculate, and the original alloy wheels are completely free of curb rash. Included are both sets of keys, the original window sticker, and all factory manuals. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks, smells, and drives exactly as it did the day it left the dealership floor.",
